<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../static/src/board.css"/>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>체스 게임</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="src/board.css"/>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="chess">
        <img src ="images/chessBoard.png" id="chessBoard"/>
        <div class="pieces">
            {{#this.squares}}
            <img src="images/{{this.symbol}}.png" id="{{this.position}}"/>
            {{/this.squares}}
        </div>
        <form action="/game" method="post">
            <br />
            {{this.player}} 차례입니다.
            <br />
            > 게임 종료 : end
            <br />
            > 이동 : move source위치 target위치 - 예. move b2 b3
            <br />
            > 게임이 종료되면 아무키나 입력하세요.
            <br />
            <br />
            {{this.message}}
            <br />
            입력하세요: <input type="text" name="command" />
            <input type="submit" />
        </form>
        <br />
        실행한 명령어 목록
        <div>
        {{this.commands}}<br />
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>